Description:
5 ACRES OF PRIME LAND IN KEILOR NORTH!
Located on a massive five acre allotment in Keilor North, this is your opportunity to seize your own slice of the quiet life without the hassles of long travels to the countryside.
The options are endless with this family home, comprising of 5 bedrooms centered around the indoor pool, large living areas blended with old world country charm.
Ready for new owners to renovate and update, or demolish and build your dream home, this property presents endless potential for the person with the right eye.
The land also carries a tennis court, large garage/workshop and a good sized dam. With easy access to the Calder freeway and only approximately 20 minutes to the city, this is an opportunity not to be missed.
It is extremely rare for a block of this size to become available this close to the city so do not expect it to sit around on the market for too long!

SPACIOUS AND STYLISH INDOOR / OUTDOOR FAMILY LIVING!
In a blissfully quiet court location, this incredibly well-built home presents a family-focused environment of quality and flexibility with easy access to Keilors enviable lifestyle attractions. Expansive two-level floorplan comprises four bedrooms (master with WIR and modern semi-ensuite bathroom), marble-tiled main family bathroom, formal lounge and dining, granite-bench kitchen and adjoining meals/family area as well as a huge rumpus/theatre room complete with bar. Close to local parks, public transport, freeway access, St Augustines Primary School and Overnewton College, Keilor Village shops and eateries. Land approx 788sqm.

Description:
IMPRESSIVE FAMILY LIVING INSIDE AND OUT!
In an exclusive Keilor Village location, this enormous home makes an ideal choice for growing families with its versatile accommodation and fabulous outdoor entertaining areas. Vast interior highlights three large bedrooms (with robes) and study/fourth bedroom, master ensuite and main bathroom, huge formal lounge, open living/dining area, granite-bench kitchen with stainless steel appliances, rumpus/second living area, big laundry and guest powder room. Other features include ducted heating and cooling, hardwood floors, extensive storage facilities throughout, plus front balcony with elevated valley views, undercover decked entertaining area, solar heated pool/spa, double garage (remote) with attic storeroom. A terrific home in a family-focused neighbourhood, its close to village parks, shops and cafes, public transport and easy freeway access. Land approx 644sqm.

Description:
OUTSTANDING!
Beautifully renovated four bedroom home ready to move in and enjoy is what this home and location have to offer. Polished timber floors along with split system cooling, carport and garage/ workshop complete the home. Close to local schools, parks and minutes away from Keilor Village, inspection recommended.
